msgid "0:僕は急ぎ足で学校へ向かっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "0:I hurried to school.[%p]"

msgid "100:周囲を見回して、人の姿がないかを確かめる。[linebreak]誰かが僕に向かって迫ってこようものなら、全力で逃げるつもりだった。[%p]"
msgstr "100:I looked around carefully to make sure no one was around me. If anybody was following me, I was going to run away as fast as I could.[%p]"

msgid "200:さっきから、ずっと過呼吸状態だ。[linebreak]ゼイゼイと、僕ののどがあえぐような音を出している。[linebreak]拭っても拭っても、額からは汗がにじみ出てくる。[%p]"
msgstr "200:I was already out of breath. My chest was heaving with each step. I kept wiping away the sweat on my forehead, and it kept coming back.[%p]"

msgid "300:学校へ行くんだ……。[linebreak]学校へ行って、意地でもこずぴぃに助けてもらうんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "300:I had to get to school. I had to get to school, and find some way to force Kozupii to help me.[%p]"

msgid "400:僕に精神攻撃してくるヤツらを、こずぴぃに殺してもらいたいぐらいだ。[linebreak]こずぴぃならやってくれる。だって彼女は壊れてるんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "400:I wanted Kozupii to kill whoever was doing this to me. Kozupii would do it. She was broken, after all.[%p]"

msgid "500:殺してやりたい……。[linebreak]殺してやりたい……！[%p]"
msgstr "500:I wanted to kill them. I wanted to kill them![%p]"

msgid "600:『将軍』とその仲間を、殺してやりたい……！[linebreak]昨日、僕のベースに来た連中だって間違いなく『将軍』とその部下だ。[%p]"
msgstr "600:I wanted to kill Shogun, and all his friends! The ones who'd visited the Base last night were clearly working for him.[%p]"

msgid "700:あいつら、ついに本気を出してきたんだ。[linebreak]僕を標的にして、僕を徹底的に消耗させた後、最後に容赦なく残酷に殺すつもりだ。[%p]"
msgstr "700:They were finally ready to go on the offensive for real. They'd made me their target, and after wearing me down, they were ready to move in for a merciless kill.[%p]"

msgid "800:そんなのイヤだ。死にたくない……。[linebreak]だから殺される前に殺すしか――[%p]"
msgstr "800:I didn't want to die… so I'd have to kill them first.[%p]"

msgid "900:また、音……！[%p]"
msgstr "900:And again, the sound![%p]"

msgid "1000:真後ろから、昨日さんざん聞いたあの軋むような音がした。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:The creaking sound I'd heard so many times yesterday, right behind me.[%p]"

msgid "1100:ビクッとして振り返る。[linebreak]でも誰もいない。車椅子なんてどこにも見当たらない。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:I turned around. But nobody was there. There was no wheelchair to be seen anywhere.[%p]"

msgid "1200:幻聴じゃない。はっきり聞こえたのに……！[%p]"
msgstr "1200:I wasn't hearing things! I heard it clearly.[%p]"

msgid "1300:また『将軍』からの攻撃か！？[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Was Shogun attacking me again?[%p]"

msgid "1400:走り出す。とにかく１人でいたくなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:I started running. I didn't want to be alone.[%p]"

msgid "1500:でも――[%p]"
msgstr "1500:But...[%p]"

msgid "1600:追いかけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:It followed me.[%p]"

msgid "1700:音が、僕のすぐ真後ろにぴったり張り付いている。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:The sound was always right behind me, no matter where I went.[%p]"

msgid "1800:やめろ、こっちに来るな……僕に近づくな……僕を見るな……！[%p]"
msgstr "1800:Stop it. Leave me alone. Stay away... Don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "1900:おかしくなりそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:I was going crazy.[%p]"

msgid "2000:もう一度振り返る勇気はなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:I didn't have the courage to look behind me again.[%p]"

msgid "2100:校門にたどり着く。[linebreak]まだ始業のチャイムは鳴っていない。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:I reached the school gate. The bell hadn't rung yet.[%p]"

msgid "2200:遅刻間際のはずだけど、ちらほらと登校してくる生徒の姿も見える。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:I was on the verge of being late, but there were still students around me, heading to their classes.[%p]"

msgid "2300:人の姿を見ただけで、ひるんでしまう。[linebreak]だけどここを通らないとこずぴぃに会えない。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:Just seeing them made me shrink back. But if I didn't go through the gate, I couldn't see Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "2400:意を決して校内に入ろうとして――[%p]"
msgstr "2400:I was about to force myself to head inside when...[%p]"

msgid "2500:またも、音。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:The sound. Again.[%p]"

msgid "2600:今度は車椅子じゃなくて、ケータイカメラのシャッター音。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:This time it was a cell phone shutter sound, not a wheelchair.[%p]"

msgid "2700:周囲へ視線を巡らせる。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:I looked around.[%p]"

msgid "2800:誰だ？\u3000誰が撮った？[%p]"
msgstr "2800:Who? Who'd taken the photo?[%p]"

msgid "2900:誰も僕を見ていない。[linebreak]ケータイを取り出しているヤツもいない。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:Nobody was looking at me. Nobody had their phone out.[%p]"

msgid "3000:なんなんだ、なんなんだよっ！[%p]"
msgstr "3000:What the hell was going on?[%p]"

msgid "3100:僕は耳を塞ぐと、周りに目もくれずに走った。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:I covered my ears and ran as fast as I could.[%p]"

msgid "3200:教室まで一気にたどり着く。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:I ran straight to my classroom.[%p]"

msgid "3300:中に駆け込もうとして、慌てて立ち止まり、その場で回れ右。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:I went to head inside, before stopping and turning around.[%p]"

msgid "3400:クラスのＤＱＮどもがたむろしていた。[linebreak]目が合いそうになったから、入るのをやめた。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:The class's DQNs were sitting near the door. Going in meant looking them in the eye. So, I didn't.[%p]"

msgid "3500:ちくしょう……。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:Damn it.[%p]"

msgid "3600:この世界は敵だらけだ。[linebreak]全員敵なんだ。死ね。どいつもこいつも死ねよっ。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:The world was full of enemies. Everyone was my enemy. Die. All of you, die.[%p]"

msgid "3700:脳内でＤＱＮどもを惨殺する妄想をしつつ、廊下を引き返す。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:I headed back into the hallway, delusions of their horrible deaths filling my mind.[%p]"

msgid "3800:チラッと見ただけだけど、こずぴぃの姿はなかった。[linebreak]と言うか、教室には女子が１人もいなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:I'd had enough time to take a quick glance inside the classroom, and Kozupii wasn't there. Actually, there wasn't a single girl in the classroom.[%p]"

msgid "3900:それはすごく奇妙な気がしたけど、どうでもよかった。[linebreak]こずぴぃがどこにいるのかだけが気になった。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:It felt really weird, but I didn't care. I only cared about where Kozupii was.[%p]"

msgid "4000:どうしてこういうときに限って、すぐに見つからないんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Why wasn't she here on the one day I needed her?[%p]"

msgid "4100:まだ、僕ののどはゼイゼイという荒い呼吸を繰り返している。[linebreak]その僕を見て、廊下を歩く生徒たちがギョッとして振り返ってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:My throat still hurt from all the wheezing, and I was out of breath. Some of the students in the hallway turned around to look at me in surprise.[%p]"

msgid "4200:[margin top="266"][center]――僕を見るな。[unk19 index="30"]"
msgstr "4200:[margin top="266"][center]—Don't look at me.[unk19 index="30"]"

msgid "4300:また音。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:The sound again.[%p]"

msgid "4400:振り返ると、見たこともないＤＱＮ男子が４人ほど、僕を見てニヤニヤしていた。ケータイをこっちに向けている。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:I turned around to see four DQN boys I'd never laid eyes on before grinning at me. They had their phones pointed in my direction.[%p]"

msgid "4500:――僕を見るな！[%p]"
msgstr "4500:—Don't look at me![%p]"

msgid "4600:ＤＱＮは無視。[linebreak]後でこずぴぃに殺してもらえばいい。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:I ignored them. I could just have Kozupii kill them later.[%p]"

msgid "4700:そんな妄想をする。とても甘美で爽快な妄想。[linebreak]どいつもこいつも死ねばいい。[linebreak]こんな世界、もううんざりだ！[%p]"
msgstr "4700:I created a delusion of it happening. It was such a sweet, pleasant delusion. I wished all of them would just die. I was just so sick of this world![%p]"

msgid "4800:こずぴぃは見当たらない。[linebreak]どこにいるのかさっぱり分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:I couldn't find Kozupii anywhere. I had no idea where she was.[%p]"

msgid "4900:もしかしたら今日は学校に来てないんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:Maybe she wasn't at school today?[%p]"

msgid "5000:だとしたらどうしよう……。[linebreak]明日まで１人で『将軍』からの精神攻撃に耐えきれる自信はなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:If that was the case, then what should I do? I didn't think I could handle Shogun's psychological attacks until tomorrow.[%p]"

msgid "5100:心の中では強がっているけど、今でさえ膝が震えて、気を抜くとその場にへたり込んでしまいそうなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:No matter how strong I tried to be, my knees were still knocking, and if I wasn't careful, I might collapse where I stood.[%p]"

msgid "5200:こずぴぃ……どこなの……？[linebreak]どこにいるんだよ……！[linebreak]僕を助けてよ……！[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Kozupii, where are you? Where are you? I need your help![%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]梢[line]「助けて……」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]梢[line]Help me...[%p]"

msgid "5400:ハッとして立ち止まった。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:I stopped.[%p]"

msgid "5500:声が聞こえた。[linebreak]しかも頭の中に直接響いてきた、心の声。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:I heard a voice. A voice inside my mind.[%p]"

msgid "5600:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃのせいじゃない……こずぴぃのせいじゃないもん……」[%p]"
msgstr "5600:[name]梢[line]It's not Kozupii's fault... It's not Kozupii's fault...[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]梢[line]「助けて……」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]梢[line]Help me...[%p]"

msgid "5800:こずぴぃ、どこだ！？[%p]"
msgstr "5800:Kozupii, where are you?[%p]"

msgid "5900:周囲を見回すと、昇降口の隅にうずくまり頭を抱えているこずぴぃの姿を見つけた。[linebreak]その姿を見て、僕は思わず息を呑んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:I looked around and saw Kozupii, crouching in a ball near the entrance to the school. When I saw her, I gasped.[%p]"

msgid "6000:彼女の全身が、大量の血を浴びたかのように真っ赤だった。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Her body was red, like she was covered in blood.[%p]"

msgid "6100:いや、“ような”じゃなくて。[linebreak]これは、血そのものだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:No, not “like” she was covered in blood. She was covered in blood.[%p]"

msgid "6200:悲鳴をあげそうになった。でも声にならなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:I almost screamed, but I was too shaken to even do so.[%p]"

msgid "6300:こずぴぃ！\u3000しっかりして！\u3000こずぴぃ！[%p]"
msgstr "6300:Kozupii! Snap out of it! Kozupii![%p]"

msgid "6400:心の中で呼びかけてみると、こずぴぃがそれに気付いてのろのろと顔を上げた。目は涙で濡れて、赤く充血している。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:I called out, and Kozupii slowly looked up at me. Her eyes were bright red and wet with tears.[%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]梢[line]「うぅ……拓巳しゃん……」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]梢[line]Wah... Takumi...[%p]"

msgid "6600:そのまま、すがるように僕の腰にしがみついてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:She grabbed onto my waist.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]拓巳[line]「ちょっ、な、なにを……！」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]拓巳[line]W-What are you doing?[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんは、こずぴぃの敵？\u3000味方？」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]梢[line]Takumi, are you my enemy? My friend?[%p]"

msgid "6900:ど、どういう意味……？[%p]"
msgstr "6900:W-What do you mean?[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]梢[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "7100:聞き直してみたけど、こずぴぃは僕の胸に顔を埋めて首を左右に振るだけだ。彼女の全身にこびりついた赤黒い血が、僕の制服を汚していく。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:I asked, but she just buried her head in my chest and shook it from left to right. The blood on her body stained my uniform.[%p]"

msgid "7200:こずぴぃって、こんなに小さいんだな。[linebreak]身体も折れちゃいそうなくらいに細い。[linebreak]こうして抱きつかれて、初めて気付いた。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:I'd never really realized how tiny she was. She was so thin, I thought she might break in half. Until she'd grabbed onto me like this, I'd never noticed.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕は、こ、こずぴぃの味方だ」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'm your friend.[%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、だから、こずぴぃに助けてもらいたい……」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]拓巳[line]S-So I want you to help me.[%p]"

msgid "7500:ありのまま、僕が思ってることを言った。[linebreak]言ってることはかなり自分に都合のいいことだけど。[linebreak]こずぴぃしか、いないんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:I told her everything I'd been thinking. Of course, I arranged it in a way that was most convenient for me, though. Kozupii, you're all I've got.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃのこと、いじめない？」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]梢[line]You won't bully Kozupii?[%p]"

msgid "7700:いじめないよ……。[linebreak]それより、僕をいじめる連中から守ってほしいんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:I won't. I want you to protect me from the people who want to bully me.[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃは、守れないよぉ……」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]梢[line]Kozupii can't protect you.[%p]"

msgid "7900:でもディソードを持ってるじゃないか！[%p]"
msgstr "7900:But you've got a Di-Sword![%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]梢[line]「だってだって、あの子のこと、うまく、扱えないぷぅ……」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]梢[line]But I can't use her right, pu![%p]"

msgid "8100:あの子って、ディソードのこと？[%p]"
msgstr "8100:By “her,” you mean the Di-Sword?[%p]"

msgid "8200:その僕の問いにこずぴぃはうなずいて。[linebreak]それから、ますます身を縮こまらせた。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:Kozupii nodded at my question. And then she began to shiver.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]梢[line]「だからね、さっきのドカバキグシャーッは、こずぴぃのせいじゃ――」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]梢[line]So, the ker-bam-schwing that happened wasn't Kozupii's fault, okay?[%p]"

msgid "8400:その衝撃は、いきなりやって来た。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:The impact came out of nowhere.[%p]"

msgid "8500:脳内に、フラッシュバックのようにとある映像が炸裂する。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:A vision like a flashback exploded in my brain.[%p]"

msgid "8600:学校。屋上。赤。血の海。強烈な血の匂い。倒れているたくさんの肉片。それが元々なんだったのか理解できないくらいバラバラ。血の海の中に立ち荒い息をつくこずぴぃ。手にはディソード――[%p]"
msgstr "8600:School. The roof. Red. A sea of blood. The overpowering smell of blood. Dozens of chunks of meat, lying on the ground. Ripped apart so much, you couldn't tell what they were before. Kozupii standing in the middle of the sea of blood, panting. The Di-Sword in her hand.[%p]"

msgid "8700:ハッと我に返る。[linebreak]今のは、なんだ！？[%p]"
msgstr "8700:I came back to my senses. What did I just see?![%p]"

msgid "8800:見えていたのは学校の屋上だった。[linebreak]あの映像はなんなんだ？\u3000ただの妄想？[linebreak]それにしてはいつもと少し違った。[%p]"
msgstr "8800:That was the school's roof, I could tell that much. But what was that? Just a delusion? It felt a little different than usual.[%p]"

msgid "8900:もしかして、僕の妄想じゃなくて、こずぴぃの妄想？[linebreak]“他人の負の妄想が見えるのがギガロマニアックスだ”とかなんとか、セナが言っていたような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:Maybe it was Kozupii's delusion, and not mine? Sena said that Gigalomaniacs could see other people's negative delusions.[%p]"

msgid "9000:それに――[%p]"
msgstr "9000:And...[%p]"

msgid "9100:今、僕にしがみついているこずぴぃの全身には、どす黒い血。まだ乾いていない。痛がっている素振りを見せないから、こずぴぃがケガしてるわけじゃない。この血はこずぴぃ自身のものじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:There was also the dark blood all over Kozupii's body as she clung to me. It still wasn't dry. She didn't seem to be in pain, so she probably wasn't hurt. The blood wasn't Kozupii's, then.[%p]"

msgid "9200:これほどの量の血を浴びるような状況について、想像を巡らせてみる。[linebreak]こんなの普通じゃない。異常だ。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:I tried to think about what could cause her to be soaked with all this blood. This wasn't normal. It wasn't normal at all.[%p]"

msgid "9300:いったい、誰の血だ？[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Whose blood was this?[%p]"

msgid "9400:こずぴぃ、誰の血なんだ！？[%p]"
msgstr "9400:Kozupii, whose blood is this?![%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]梢[line]「んとぉ、こずぴぃをね、いじめた人たち……」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]梢[line]Mhnn... the people who bullied Kozupii...[%p]"

msgid "9600:こずぴぃはうなだれていた。[linebreak]僕からそっと身を離し、バツが悪そうに顔をそむけてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Her head was slumped forward. She slowly pushed away from me, and awkwardly looked away.[%p]"

msgid "9700:人差し指を唇に添えて。[linebreak]拗ねているようにも見えた。[linebreak]手にこびりついた血を舐めているようにも見えた。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:She had her index finger to her lip, like she was sulking. Or maybe like she was licking the blood on her hand.[%p]"

msgid "9800:その血は、他人の血じゃないの？[%p]"
msgstr "9800:Is that your blood?[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]梢[line]「他人の血だよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]梢[line]It's somebody else's blood.[%p]"

msgid "10000:イヤな予感がする。[linebreak]こずぴぃ、もしそれが事実なら……やり過ぎじゃないか……？[%p]"
msgstr "10000:Something felt very, very wrong. Kozupii... if that's true... do you think you maybe went a little too far?[%p]"

msgid "10100:始業ベルが鳴った。ホームルームが始まる時間だ。[linebreak]すでに周囲に生徒の姿はない。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:The first bell rang. It was time for homeroom to start. All the other students had already gone inside, and it was just the two of us out here.[%p]"

msgid "10200:僕は意を決して、教室へ向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:I worked up the courage to go back to the classroom.[%p]"

msgid "10300:誰にもバレないように、窓の外からそっと中をのぞいてみる。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:I quietly took a look through the window, making sure nobody could see me.[%p]"

msgid "10400:[name]拓巳[line]「これって……！」[%p]"
msgstr "10400:[name]拓巳[line]What the heck?![%p]"

msgid "10500:愕然としてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:I couldn't believe it.[%p]"

msgid "10600:すでにホームルームは始まっていて、担任も来てるっていうのに。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:Homeroom had started. The teacher was there.[%p]"

msgid "10700:教室内には、さっき見たときと同様、女子が一人もいない。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:But there wasn't a single girl inside the class.[%p]"

msgid "10800:嘘だろ……。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:No...[%p]"

msgid "10900:確かめなきゃ。それがただの妄想だって、確かめなきゃ。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:I had to make sure. I had to make sure it was just a delusion.[%p]"

msgid "11000:屋上まで駆け上がり、勢いよく扉を開けた。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:I ran up the stairs to the roof and flung open the door.[%p]"

msgid "11100:最初に目に飛び込んできたのは、くすんだ青空。[linebreak]そしてその後から――[%p]"
msgstr "11100:The first thing I saw was a dreary blue sky. And then...[%p]"

msgid "11200:鮮烈な赤。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:A brilliant red.[%p]"

msgid "11300:文字通りの血の海。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:A literal sea of blood.[%p]"

msgid "11400:そのあまりの惨状と、生理的な嫌悪感と、おぞましさと、強烈な異臭に、たまらず嘔吐していた。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:I threw up on the spot from a mix of terror, physical revulsion, and the sheer stench.[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんは、こずぴぃの味方だよね……？」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]梢[line]Takumi, you're my friend, right?[%p]"

msgid "11600:ハッとする。[linebreak]振り向くと、背後にこずぴぃが立っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:I gasped. I turned around and Kozupii was standing there.[%p]"

msgid "11700:彼女は目尻に涙を浮かべながらも。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:She had tears in her eyes, but...[%p]"

msgid "11800:僕に向かって――[%p]"
msgstr "11800:She was looking at me—[%p]"

msgid "11900:血まみれのままで――[%p]"
msgstr "11900:Covered in blood—[%p]"

msgid "12000:無邪気に笑った。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:And smiling innocently.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]拓巳[line]「うわあああ！」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]拓巳[line]Uwah![%p]"

